task.summary: Default task
Initial Commit
- improved director timer and tests, so they are more deterministic - implemented system auto event registration - implemented system configure method
- implemented factory system
- systems now use typeId instead of category for identity
- Added AMD support
- Fixed auto spawn event in Factory - Fixed error thrown by requireJs hook - Construct can now extend properties - Director refactored to use properties instead closure functions - Readme updated
- EntityManager refactored to use properties instead closure functions
- SystemManager refactored to use properties instead of closure functions - EventManager refactored to use properties instead of closure functions
- Entity, Component, System, and Factory refactored to use properties instead of closure functions - Static properties support added to Construct
- Added despawn to factory
- Fixed destroy method on System, so that it can be overridden.
- Converted fullName from a function to a property on Constructors
- Moved todo to issue tracker
Added render in addition to update.
Implemented Map for object tracking
Merged map functionality into Construct object.
Added support for entity hierarchy
Added Construct.create and construct.destroy functions
Add/Remove component now emits named event if the component has a fullName.
Fixed bug in systems.removeAll where an error occurred if a system had previously been removed.
Refactored component.serialize to base keys off defaults/properties in the prototype. Added keys function that returns the serializable keys.
Fixed bug where dirtyable properties shared storage across instances.
Added code coverage to unit tests. Filled in missing unit tests. Fixed minor bugs exposed by missing tests. Added event to entity.addChild/removeChild
Resolved bug where component.keys return entity & valid if the derived class did not provide properties.
Components are now observable. Dirtyable properties will trigger any listeners.
Converted project from single source file to multi-file amd source. Added build.
Added module for RC4 based random number generator
Added optional fixed frame rate option for time step. Added entity.all method.
Updated intro/outro
Updated build.
Fixed timer issue on iOS
Added project description. Moved API references to JSDocs.
Refactored component API on the Entity class.
Fixed line feed
Added compatibility section.
Added JSDoc stubs to objects
Added JSDoc output to repository
Updated docs with repro and doc links
